==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Auxetophone
<hw>Aux*e"to*phone</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ that
may be increased + <?/ sound, voice.]</ety> <def>A pneumatic reproducer
for a phonograph, controlled by the recording stylus on the principle of
the relay. It produces much clearer and louder tones than does the
ordinary vibrating disk reproducer.</def> <mark>[obsolescent]</mark>
⟦br⟧
